Hi,

Thanks for writing to Dr. Math.

Roulette is a losing game, on average. Because of the presence of the
0 and 00 spots, the house has an edge. If you want more information
about roulette, try the Wizard of Odds:

  http://wizardofodds.com/games/roulette.html

Does this help?  Please feel free to write back with any questions you
may have.

- Doctor Roy, The Math Forum
  <http://mathforum.org/dr.math/>

